==English==
===Pronunciation===
*psī, /psaɪ/, /<tt>psaI</tt>/ ''or'' sī, /saɪ/, /<tt>saI</tt>/
{{rfap}}

====Prounciation note====
*In contexts where confusion might arise with the Greek letter '''[[xi]]''', which also has sī, /saɪ/, /<tt>saI</tt>/ as a possible pronunciation, the pronunciation of '''psi''' in which the ''p'' is pronounced is preferable.

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg-both}}

#(''countable'') The twenty-third letter of [[Classical Greek|Classical]] and [[Modern Greek]] and the twenty-fourth letter of [[Old Greek|Old]] and [[Ancient Greek]].
#(''uncountable'') A form of [[psychic]] energy.

*Letter of the Greek alphabet: '''&#936; &#968;
**Previous: [[chi|&#935;]]
**Next: [[omega|&#937;]]

